                Mr. Arthur Greenwood  (Wakefield)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-50935f1f-0b56-441d-9eeb-9fcaba2aec79" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
