<p class="">I presume that by "the enemy," my hon. Friend means the Ger- <span id="453" class="column-number" data-column-number="453"></span> mans. I made it perfectly clear that I supported the policy of the Government for the unconditional surrender of the enemy.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
