<p class="">It is a case of— <blockquote><q>"they are all mad but me and thee, and thou art a little bit queer."</q></blockquote></p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a01aecf1-2851-48dc-b451-c59878126b59" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
