        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Oh, Drew Pearson again.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-50037f4b-98e5-450a-a5b5-a5d0954551d8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
